{"tid":376891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"激搶手　大學生IT空缺增4成","createTime":"2017-08-27T10:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T14:29:59.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24ce9f3ffc3e860be8d98bde84f0dcb1e89a729a","tid":376891,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:23:19.000Z","msg":"剛畢業的應屆大學生不愁無工做，其中資訊科技界大量吸納畢業生，據8大院校聯校就業資料庫數據顯示，資訊科技業於今年5至7月的空缺高達近4,000份，按年升43%。<br />\n<br />\n有人力顧問表示，今年畢業生求職較去年容易，金融、銀行、專業服務等行業空缺多，願吸納新人；而IT業年資淺的職位，一向難請人，起薪最高達1.5萬元。有學者指出，今年及明年均為本港勞動力短缺高峰期，料失業率今年下半年仍會在低位徘徊。<br />\n<br />\n統計處昨日公布，今年5至7月失業率維持3.1%，就業不足率則下跌0.1個百分點至1.1%，創20年新低。勞工及福利局局長羅致光表示，本港勞工市場保持全民就業，因本地需求堅穩、訪港旅遊業改善，零售、住宿及餐飲服務業等與消費、旅遊相關行業的失業率，進一步下跌 0.1個百分點至4.6%，是自2015年底後的最低水平。<br />\n<br />\n據大學聯校就業資料庫數據，於5至7月期間，資訊科技、電訊及科技行業錄得最多空缺，達3,973份，按年增加43%；其次是銀行、金融服務及保險（見表）。數據亦顯示，今年1至7月錄得4.3萬份空缺，按年同期上升4.5%，大學畢業生平均月薪為14,629元。<br />\n<br />\n安俊人力資源顧問董事總經理周綺萍表示，IT業一向難請新人，資歷要求較淺的職位多，入職薪酬由1.3萬至1.5萬元，若申請人精於手機App開發、雲端應用、大數據、網絡安全等範疇，尤其吃香，或可叫價更高。<br />\n<br />\n她透露，兩周前其公司協助一名只有1年工作經驗的計算機科學系畢業生跳槽，由房地產轉到金融機構做IT支援人員，加薪逾1成至1.5萬元；她表示，一般求職者少於2年轉工一次，會被視為「份工做唔長」，惟因IT業招聘太難，即使只有1年工作經驗，亦能輕易轉工。<br />\n<br />\n她又指出，今年畢業生求職較往年容易，銀行、金融等行業願吸納新人，提供不少空缺月薪1萬至1.4萬元；而會計、法律等專業服務，亦招攬管理實習生，起薪與工程業一樣，達1.5萬至2.5萬元。但她提醒，畢業生若在8月仍未成功找工，須加緊步伐：「8月應該要入職，9月供畢業生的空缺更少！」<br />\n<br />\n中文大學劉佐德全球經濟及金融研究所常務所長莊太量表示，本港上半年經濟強力反彈，外圍環境穩定，加上人口老化，本港不開放輸入外勞，今、明兩年是勞動力短缺高峰期，預料失業率下半年保持低位。"},{"pid":"b0c4bc72d044d7dd5747bfa2ddc0a4ac5028fecc","tid":376891,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:24:02.000Z","msg":"老貓不願接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685f9ddb48ca9fe1ee0115cc7b0b0ac7e11d11ea","tid":376891,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:24:24.000Z","msg":"炒撚晒咪有位囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4542576cc4ae0c5855a751b7a96788b2d2d758b3","tid":376891,"uid":522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"轉個頭又成個IT dept炒哂"},{"pid":"bdb89bef3c206fdd5e0e19a919e62041fca7b2fe","tid":376891,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:26:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老貓不願接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2ad915ab12fc8e22fc254e785fec8ebebb2a75","tid":376891,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:27:24.000Z","msg":"今年香港各大公司加埋都炒左五百個IT人<br />\n有d成個部門搬去第二度<br />\n係香港千奇唔好做IT"},{"pid":"495059c09b3ef46bb7d88bf051514016723924d7","tid":376891,"uid":75647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:30:06.000Z","msg":"我是幸福的IT 人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee3d89b3122671f6b9ed8e27b72e9c7eca70d4d","tid":376891,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:30:08.000Z","msg":"老貓唔敢入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cb5436ae05a6f4cc2423190ef71a2a4d11495d","tid":376891,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74be9d1110b0f7d64e9574662a46c5dfa177818","tid":376891,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又有機構裁減資訊科技（IT）員工！《路透社》引述兩名消息人士報道，<span style=\"color: red;\">保險公司AXA安盛在港裁250人，全部均是IT員工，原因是削減成本，而香港原本是AXA亞洲區的IT總部。</span><br />\n<br />\n裁員行動在本周四發生，AXA並同時移師至菲律賓馬尼拉及馬來西亞吉隆坡，在兩處設立資訊科技中心，分別聘請300人及110人，並形容在這些地區設立IT部是「在可負擔的成本上增強部門效能」。<br />\n<br />\nAXA發言人並無確認或否認裁員一事，僅指出AXA恒常地審視業務，以提升產品種類及服務，並於亞洲建立科技平台，致力提升科技水平及效能，中間或會牽涉部分區域的人手重整。<br />\n<br />\n資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑指出，不少企業因應減省成本，加上香港人工貴，租金貴，故此一些工序由其他地區取代，不過他認為，大企業在裁員前，必須要慎重考慮是否有其他安排，例如內部轉職，否則對其形象並不好。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">今年IT人被企業開刀屬等閒事，例如國泰航空今年5月裁190名經理級以上員工，IT部是重災區，人數多達77人，主要是削減成本考慮。滙豐今年3月有逾百名IT員工收「大信封」，當時發言人回應指，削減成本為該行策略一部份，以確保競爭力及維持運作效率。</span><br />\n<br />\nAXA亦於2014年以26億元作價，將香港強積金業務轉售予美國信安，不過當時並未有牽涉裁員。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57128347&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57128347%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170825&d=DIpaSCtE0DfNn%2F2xwRNnF4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d262b0d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57128347%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170825&h=065e9153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57128347&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170825</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bc50e60a784e15a79ccd142553a9a40702f4003f","tid":376891,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:33:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做it=幸福"},{"pid":"edce560b5687fed26850a94c1aba13ded92f41af","tid":376891,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:34:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ae4c5ed43279750d0c406a45c8d39941dfbb0af","tid":376891,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年香港各大公司加埋都炒左五百個IT人<br />\n有d成個部門搬去第二度<br />\n係香港千奇唔好做IT</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a56feac93333cdaaccfd4050bb40199488fc9e","tid":376891,"uid":43483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>fg 唔怕無工做<br />\n不過頂多做廿年<br />\n之後就會俾人炒<br />\n你睇近年 AXA, CX, HSBC 間間都係大公司<br />\n間間都炒晒it 部所有人<br />\n下至上都無得留低<br />\n無辦法，it 呢行5年一少變十年一大變<br />\n二個大變已經改頭換面<br />\n難聽d 講，炒左你，請番幾個fg 仲有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到時你抯住垃圾經驗，出去無人請只能做看更<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家有最低工資看更都隨時多過it fresh grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4021634a7cfbbed63b83cd63a85385bb3c70fb56","tid":376891,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779d2ca8b5301fe2f150f694988c023e4e63c7fa","tid":376891,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做it=幸福</blockquote><br />\nAgree"},{"pid":"b8bfa8a3a01885f967c8770d9bb03f47e4903a15","tid":376891,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" clas